data.description: This home shows like a model! Kitchen features granite, a huge island, lots of storage and matching stainless appliances. Seller added under counter custom lighting. Open floor plan living room features a gas fireplace with remote and color/lighting settings as well as a beautiful view of the lushly landscaped backyard. Master bedroom is spacious and includes double sinks, granite and a snail shower in master bath. Back patio and backyard are a private oasis with a water feature and a hot tub that could convey with the home home. Garage is a 3+ and has built in workbench and floor to ceiling storage cabinets. In addition to the laundry room, there is a separate mud room off of garage. Home also features recirculating hot water, 11 foot ceilings and so many more upgrades!
